data.title: Britannia
data.meta_description: Britannia  - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses the biscuit industry in India. It notes that the organized sector produces around 60% of biscuits while the unorganized sector produces 40%. The biscuit industry has an annual turnover of around Rs. 3000 crores and is one of the largest food industries in India. It also provides details about the history of biscuit production in India and the processes involved in manufacturing biscuits.
